[0.001, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;64r\u001b8\u001bM\u001b[1;67r\u001b[2;1H; configuring many of the aspects of PHP's behavior.\r"]
[0.033, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[?1c"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[?25h\u001b[?0c"]
[0.001, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;64r\u001b8\u001bM\u001b[1;67r\u001b[2;1H"]
[0.001, "o", "; PHP's initialization file, generally called php.ini, is responsible for\r"]
